hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiMediumThreshold.description: The medium signal threshold of CMDA 1xRTT RSSI. The absolute value of hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiMediumThreshold should be less than or equal to the absolute value of hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiWeakThreshold (|hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiMediumThreshold| <= |hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiWeakThreshold|).

hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiWeakThreshold.name: hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiWeakThreshold
hh3c3GCdma1xRttRssiWeakThreshold.description: The weak signal threshold of CMDA 1xRTT RSSI. hh3c3GCdmaEvDoRssiMediumThreshold.description: The medium signal threshold of CMDA EvDo RSSI.
